<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Peter Falkensteiner von Falkenfels</head><p>Der Rat bittet, die Antwort des Weinmar Ecker auf den Vermittlungsversuch von Heinrich Nothafft einzuholen, sofern Ecker nicht bereits geantwortet hat, und weiterzuleiten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_91" id="45v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_91_r1l20"><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Valkenſteiner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_91_r1l21"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> valkenſteıner Vns hat <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft vıcʒtum Jn <expan>nıd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> peyern nehſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l22"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / vvıe er vveynmer Eker <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wölt von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprüch <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l23">
<add><expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan></add> Eker ʒu vns meynt ʒe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / dıe ſache gen vns in gut anʒuſteen laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l24">So wölt er dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Eker vnd auch vns tag <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> für ſıch <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l25">ſo er des müſſıg möcht geſein . Nu als der <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> vıcʒtum neẅlıch hıe ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l26"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> geweſt ıſt <expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnd vom Rat ʒu Jm geſchıkt ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_91_r1l27">erfarn vvas Jm der Eker <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hett / der hat <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>freẅnd<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_92" id="46r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l1">verſteen <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ Jm der <expan>eg<ex>e</ex>n<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> Eker noch nıht <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l2">er hab . <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> befolhen . <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> antwurt von dem Eker <expan>einʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l3"><expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch mıt fleıſſ <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> daʒ eẅch der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Eker noch nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l4"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hett / daʒ Jr denn dıe antwurt von Jm <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l5">vns dıe 
<del rend="strikethrough">wellet ʒu wıſſen tun </del> bey dıſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> oder bey eẅr ſelbs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l6"><expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſo welln </del> auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> koſte wellet ʒu wıſſen tun . Vnd vns darinn <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l7">guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweıſet als wır eẅch wol getrawen . Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvır etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_92_r1l8"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Leonhardȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_91" id="45v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Valkensteiner </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Valkensteiner, uns hat
                            <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft, vicztum in
                            <expan>Nid<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Peyern, nehst
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, wie er Weynmer Eker
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wölt von
                                <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> sprüch
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die
                            <add><expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan></add> Eker zu uns meynt ze
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, die sache gen uns in gut anzusteen
                        lassen; so wölt er dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Eker und auch uns
                        tag <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> für sich
                            <expan>beschaid<ex>en,</ex></expan> so er des müssig möcht gesein. Nu
                        als der <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> vicztum newlich hie zu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> gewest ist,
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd
                        vom rat zu im geschikt zu erfarn, was im der Eker
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hett; der hat
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <pb facs="#facs_92" id="46r"/>versteen
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz im der
                                <expan>eg<ex>e</ex>n<ex>an</ex>t<ex>e</ex></expan> Eker noch niht
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hab, und er hab
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> befolhen,
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> antwurt von dem Eker
                                <expan>einzuneme<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch mit fleiss,
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz ewch der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Eker noch niht
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hett, daz ir denn die antwurt von im
                                <expan>erford<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und uns die bey disem
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> oder bey ewr selbs
                            <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> koste
                        wellet zu wissen tun und uns darinn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten
                                <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beweiset, als wir ewch wol getrawen.
                        Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Leonhardi. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
